_sText:
''High above these jungles, battles rage atop a strange arena platform in the skies...''

----

Changes from 1v1_ascension include:

-Increased max player count per team from 6 to 12

-Modified the lower levels to keep players from falling off the narrow catwalks too easily

-Added more cover to the two side-platforms, turning them into proper sniper nests

-Hollowed out the central platform and added a healing device to this new room

-Changed the skybox and added a massive jungle 3D skybox

----

Ascension2 is ideal for both one-on-one matches and small team battles.

Put the map in cstrike\maps.
